@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fyrmrz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(v2)
    v1 = (0.95 + 0.65)
    tmp = (wp.sin(v0) * 0.31)
    v2 = (v2 + (v2 * (tmp + 0.70 - v2 + 0.64)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.27 * v0 + 0.58)))
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.94 / v1 + 0.38)) - wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.90)))
    data[tid] = v0
